<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空盯着前面的山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有朵红云总是出现在那山上。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里一定有妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这路是通往前面那座山的。”唐僧紧张地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空点点头说：“我们必须小心点。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抽出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净举起了宝仗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒也拿起了钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们小心翼翼地往前走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个妖怪坐在山顶上，看着他们慢慢靠近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧终于到了。”妖怪自言自语，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听说只要吃上一口唐僧肉，就可以长生不老。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那妖怪又看了看唐僧他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哦！那和尚的徒弟们都拿出了兵器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们可能看到我的红云了。我得伪装一下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪变成了一个小男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑下山，坐在路边等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，唐僧一行人就到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧看到了小男孩儿，立刻从马上下来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，那是个妖怪。”悟空警告说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧瞪着悟空。“他只是个孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身问男孩儿，“你怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“强盗抢劫了我的家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿说，“请帮帮我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你是谁！”悟空大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是个妖怪！我不会让你吃了唐僧的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿看上去非常害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！”唐僧厉声说，“你吓坏他了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，你又上当了！”悟空大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你总是被妖怪骗，却从不相信我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“安静，悟空。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不然，我就要念紧箍咒了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空生气地瞪着那个小男孩儿，但也没再说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧扶小男孩儿站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能走吗？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿摇摇头说：“我的腿受伤了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧招手让悟空过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你背着他吧。不要对他太过分了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一行人继续往西走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空背着那小男孩儿。悟空走得很慢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，就远远地落在了后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你骗了唐僧。”悟空对小男孩儿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但你骗不了我。我知道你是个妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道你在说什么。”小男孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一阵大风吹过，大树被连根拔起，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>差一点儿就击中了悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“我知道是你吹的这风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>使出你所有的招术吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你决不可能把我吹跑的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天兵天将都没打败我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走到了悬崖边缘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空向悬崖下面看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要把你从这悬崖上扔下去。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会告诉唐僧你跑了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当悟空要把小男孩儿从自己背上抓下来时，小男孩儿消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“他一定是害怕了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，风变得更大了，四处尘土飞扬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空听到尖叫声，马上跑向唐僧他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父！”悟空大喊着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尘土飞扬，悟空看不清前方。“你们在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当风停下的时候，他看到八戒和悟净躺在路边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“起风了。”八戒说着爬起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那风把我们都吹倒了。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了看四周。“师父呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！不！”八戒大喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那小男孩儿确实是个妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抓走了师父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摇摇头说：“我们都回家吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>西天取经结束了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>